00:37:56,207 --> 00:37:58,508
Kimi, did you finish
plugging all the WDC data

633
00:37:58,509 --> 00:37:59,876
into the forecast model?

634
00:37:59,877 --> 00:38:02,612
Yeah, last night. Still rendering.

