637
00:38:08,252 --> 00:38:09,519
Did we?

638
00:38:09,520 --> 00:38:10,820
No. Of course not.

639
00:38:10,821 --> 00:38:11,388
Look, uh, uh,

640
00:38:11,389 --> 00:38:13,556
go check the battery backups
in the emergency generator.

641
00:38:13,557 --> 00:38:15,859
Make sure they're online, set on auto.

642
00:38:15,860 --> 00:38:17,304
Right.

643
00:38:19,130 --> 00:38:21,731
Are we gonna lose power?

644
00:38:21,732 --> 00:38:23,500
Uh, don't worry. We're covered.

645
00:38:23,501 --> 00:38:26,503
We should be fine,
even if the public power grid goes down.

646
00:38:26,504 --> 00:38:29,883
Again? How much this time?
The whole city?

647
00:38:30,841 --> 00:38:34,220
No. The whole planet.

648
00:38:37,214 --> 00:38:38,886
They're here.

649
00:38:40,017 --> 00:38:41,217
Dr. Ward?
-Yes.

650
00:38:41,218 --> 00:38:43,019
I'm General Railen.

651
00:38:43,020 --> 00:38:45,655
This is Intel Director,
Dwight Thompson.

652
00:38:45,656 --> 00:38:48,191
We'd like to discuss the information
you relayed to the folks

653
00:38:48,192 --> 00:38:50,727
at the World Data Center
yesterday afternoon.

654
00:38:50,728 --> 00:38:52,662
Absolutely. Follow me.

655
00:38:52,663 --> 00:38:54,164
We didn't do it.
-Ethan.

656
00:38:54,165 --> 00:38:56,266
Whatever it is.

657
00:38:56,267 --> 00:38:58,337
Settle down, sonny.

658
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:03,440
Since yesterday morning,

659
00:39:03,441 --> 00:39:06,142
there's been a steady registered increase
in radiation levels

660
00:39:06,143 --> 00:39:07,510
on the planet's surface.

661
00:39:07,511 --> 00:39:10,780
We are being bombarded with
gamma radiation from the sun, as usual.

662
00:39:10,781 --> 00:39:15,218
But the amount getting through is,
uh, well, alarming.

663
00:39:15,219 --> 00:39:17,854
Wait a minute.
You're talking about solar radiation?

664
00:39:18,823 --> 00:39:21,858
I thought we had a security issue
with nuclear fallout.

665
00:39:21,859 --> 00:39:24,227
Wha- uh, nuclear fallout?

666
00:39:24,228 --> 00:39:25,628
Thank you, doctor.

667
00:39:25,629 --> 00:39:27,597
Someone on staff
is going to get an earful

668
00:39:27,598 --> 00:39:28,965
when we get back.

669
00:39:28,966 --> 00:39:31,968
But, General. This isn't just
a solar radiation problem.

670
00:39:31,969 --> 00:39:34,137
This is, it's much worse.

671
00:39:34,138 --> 00:39:35,742
Please.

672
00:39:40,411 --> 00:39:42,946
Nuclear gamma radiation contained
in the solar wind

673
00:39:42,947 --> 00:39:44,881
is mostly deflected away from Earth

674
00:39:44,882 --> 00:39:46,916
by the planet's
protective magnetic shield,

675
00:39:46,917 --> 00:39:48,351
the magnetosphere.

676
00:39:48,352 --> 00:39:50,920
Uh, now, that field is created
in the convection flows

677
00:39:50,921 --> 00:39:52,756
of molten iron in the Earth's ore,

678
00:39:52,757 --> 00:39:55,358
powered by the planet's rotation.

679
00:39:55,359 --> 00:39:57,627
Doctor, we're not all physicists here.

680
00:39:57,628 --> 00:40:00,363
What the hell are you talkin' about?

681
00:40:00,364 --> 00:40:02,866
Our shield from the sun
is getting weaker

682
00:40:02,867 --> 00:40:06,075
because the Earth's rotation
is getting slower.

683
00:40:07,304 --> 00:40:10,407
We've already slowed the equivalent
of almost 6 hours.

684
00:40:10,408 --> 00:40:11,541
How?

685
00:40:11,542 --> 00:40:14,110
Well, we've been slowing naturally
for millennia.

686
00:40:14,111 --> 00:40:15,912
I- just over the past century,

687
00:40:15,913 --> 00:40:19,860
the Earth's magnetic field
has weakened by about 5%

688
00:40:19,917 --> 00:40:23,887
But something's been triggered.
Something has put on the brakes.

689
00:40:23,888 --> 00:40:25,924
What would cause that?

690
00:40:26,590 --> 00:40:29,292
Uh, well, um, I don't, uh,

691
00:40:29,293 --> 00:40:31,027
I don't have enough hard data to know.

692
00:40:31,028 --> 00:40:32,629
Well, what's your theory?

693
00:40:32,630 --> 00:40:34,864
You must have some idea.

694
00:40:34,865 --> 00:40:36,633
General, I don't deal in guesswork.

695
00:40:36,634 --> 00:40:39,102
Um, it's been suggested that

696
00:40:39,103 --> 00:40:41,571
a disruption of the planet's
core field forces

697
00:40:41,572 --> 00:40:43,706
could be caused
by a large magnetic incident

698
00:40:43,707 --> 00:40:46,976
occurring near one of several key nodes
on the planetary grid.

699
00:40:46,977 --> 00:40:49,115
What kind of incident?

700
00:40:49,346 --> 00:40:52,615
An intense gravitational field
from a near-miss asteroid,

701
00:40:52,616 --> 00:40:57,720
a massive meteor strike,
an electromagnetic pulse of some kind?

702
00:40:57,721 --> 00:40:59,322
An EMP?

703
00:40:59,323 --> 00:41:01,157
Like the one created
in a nuclear blast?

704
00:41:01,158 --> 00:41:02,525
It's afar-fetched theory.

705
00:41:02,526 --> 00:41:05,361
There is no hard evidence
to support that finding.

706
00:41:05,362 --> 00:41:06,663
I don't know.

707
00:41:06,664 --> 00:41:09,405
Doesn't sound too far-fetched to me.

708
00:41:10,301 --> 00:41:13,102
All right. This office
and all of its contents

709
00:41:13,103 --> 00:41:16,773
are now classified top secret
in the interest of national security.

710
00:41:16,774 --> 00:41:18,208
The 3 of you will be given clearance

711
00:41:18,209 --> 00:41:20,510
so you can continue
analyzing the situation.

712
00:41:20,511 --> 00:41:23,046
But at no point will you communicate
any of your findings

713
00:41:23,047 --> 00:41:24,747
to anyone outside of this room.

714
00:41:24,748 --> 00:41:26,850
From now on, you report only to me.

715
00:41:26,851 --> 00:41:28,017
Is that understood?

716
00:41:28,018 --> 00:41:30,520
Just a minute. They don't work for you.

717
00:41:30,521 --> 00:41:32,922
And if we're about to have
a major global crisis,

718
00:41:32,923 --> 00:41:34,457
I- I don't want them stuck here
in the city.

719
00:41:34,458 --> 00:41:36,693
They need to go home,
be with their families.

720
00:41:36,694 --> 00:41:39,462
Oh, that's really sweet, doctor.
It really is.

721
00:41:39,463 --> 00:41:42,065
But we don't have time
for those kind of niceties.

722
00:41:42,066 --> 00:41:43,933
I need further analysis.

723
00:41:43,934 --> 00:41:46,669
And I'm not going to spend my time
getting into a contest with you

724
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:48,238
to see which one of us
has got the bigger--

725
00:41:48,239 --> 00:41:52,041
Okay. Okay, guys, that's okay.
We'll stay.

726
00:41:52,042 --> 00:41:53,476
I don't know if you've noticed,

727
00:41:53,477 --> 00:41:56,312
but, um,
this office kind of is our home

728
00:41:56,313 --> 00:41:59,415
and if it all hits the fan,

729
00:41:59,416 --> 00:42:03,086
there's no place
I'd rather be than here,

730
00:42:03,087 --> 00:42:06,189
doing the work and,
and getting the facts right.

731
00:42:06,190 --> 00:42:07,691
Yeah.

732
00:42:08,559 --> 00:42:10,436
What she said.

733
00:42:11,695 --> 00:42:13,299
Me too.

734
00:42:16,367 --> 00:42:17,433
All right.

735
00:42:17,434 --> 00:42:19,536
Finish rendering the forecast model.

736
00:42:19,537 --> 00:42:22,574
Keep an eye
on anomalous magnetic readings.

737
00:42:22,806 --> 00:42:24,683
We'll report to him.

738
00:42:29,780 --> 00:42:31,414
Now Dr. Ward,

739
00:42:31,415 --> 00:42:34,361
about this far-fetched theory,

740
00:42:34,618 --> 00:42:36,722
where do I learn more?

741
00:42:53,704 --> 00:42:54,470
Clinic?

742
00:42:54,471 --> 00:42:55,905
Dr. Ward?

743
00:42:55,906 --> 00:42:57,707
Kimi, is that you?
-Yeah.

744
00:42:57,708 --> 00:42:59,375
You're going to have to speak up.
I can't hear you.

745
00:42:59,376 --> 00:43:00,910
There's a lot of people here.

746
00:43:00,911 --> 00:43:02,412
Um, I can't talk long.

747
00:43:02,413 --> 00:43:04,981
I, um, your brother wanted me to call.

748
00:43:04,982 --> 00:43:06,215
Is he all right?

749
00:43:06,216 --> 00:43:07,417
Um, he's fine.

750
00:43:07,418 --> 00:43:10,820
They, um,
they took him to find Dr. Barrett.

751
00:43:10,821 --> 00:43:12,355
David? Well, who took him?

752
00:43:12,356 --> 00:43:14,357
I'm not supposed to say.

753
00:43:14,358 --> 00:43:16,225
Um, but your brother wanted me
to tell you

754
00:43:16,226 --> 00:43:18,628
