755
00:43:18,629 --> 00:43:20,496
and he will come get you
as soon as he can.

756
00:43:20,497 --> 00:43:22,065
You need to tell me what's happening.

757
00:43:22,066 --> 00:43:23,499
We have a lot of sick people here,

758
00:43:23,500 --> 00:43:26,139
